cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.DS, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with allocation mechanisms, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization and convex programming (cs.IT), as well as mathematical modeling and analysis (cs.MA). The use of rebates and budget balance is related to mechanism design (cs.DS), and the paper proposes a mechanism that is efficient and comes close to budget balance, which involves decision making and optimization (cs.AI).
